newsitem.title: UK: SOCCER-MANCHESTER UNITED V BORUSSIA DORTMUND TEAMS.
newsitem.headline: SOCCER-MANCHESTER UNITED V BORUSSIA DORTMUND TEAMS.

text.p: Line-ups for Wednesday's European Cup semifinal second leg between Manchester United and Borussia Dortmund at Old Trafford:
Manchester United: 1-Peter Schmeichel; 2-Gary Neville, 6-Gary Pallister, 4-David May, 28-Phil Neville, 5-Ronny Johnsen, 8-Nicky Butt, 10-David Beckham, 7-Eric Cantona, 9-Andy Cole, 20-Ole Solskjaer

Borussia Dortmund: 1-Stefan Klos; 15-Juergen Kohler, 20-Wolfgang Feiersinger, 16-Martin Kree, 14-Paul Lambert, 7-Stefan Reuter, 10-Andreas Moeller, 18-Lars Ricken, 17-Joerg Heinrich, 13-Karlheinz Reidle, 9-Stephane Chapuisat
